## Stella OS v1.1 — Initial Release

First public build of Stella OS.

### Highlights
- Arch-based system (Ax OS foundation)
- UEFI boot with Stella branding
- Minimal CLI live environment
- Designed for manual installation
- Clean base for customization

### Installation
This release provides a minimal live environment.  
Follow the Arch Linux installation guide:
https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Installation_guide

